The paper discusses the design and deployment of smart grid devices and control algorithms, and the need for intruder prevention and detection. This suggests a focus on cybersecurity (cs.CR) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the need for accurate predictions of human decision making, which could involve artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and game theory (cs.GT). Finally, the paper discusses the usefulness of the approach for design, which could involve software engineering (cs.SE).
